    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered for sale is a mechanically sound E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering featuring the S65 4.0L V8 with an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen utilizes individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox to deliver a visceral, linear power band. The vehicle maintains its structural rigidity with the factory carbon fiber roof and a well-sorted suspension geometry. Key enthusiast-level maintenance has been addressed, including the critical rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements, ensuring the high-revving internals remain within factory tolerances. The M Variable Differential Lock provides exceptional lockup for corner-exit traction. While displaying minor cosmetic evidence of spirited road use, the drivetrain and hydraulic steering rack offer the precise feedback expected of a true M-division product.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
