    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily reliability. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, and while there are a handful of minor stone chips on the front valence consistent with careful highway use, the body is remarkably straight and free of any significant dings. Inside, you will find a pristine, smoke-free cabin with supple leather upholstery; the driver\u2019s seat bolster shows only the slightest signs of entry-wear, while the rear seats appear nearly untouched. Every electronic feature, from the responsive touchscreen navigation to the premium audio system and dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. I have kept a comprehensive binder of all service records, including a recent full synthetic oil change, a fresh cabin air filter, and a brake system flush performed last season. The tires are matching sets with approximately 75% tread remaining, and the brakes provide a firm, confident bite with no pulsation. This is a turn-key example that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
